flowchart TD
    A[Fetch Resumes] --> B[Extract Resume Content]
    B --> C[Summarize / Vectorize Content]
    C --> D[Rank Resumes Based on Role]
    D --> E[Store Screened Resumes in DB]
    E --> F[Optional: Feedback Loop for Learning]

    subgraph Fetch
        A1[From Email / Upload / Local Folder]
        A --> A1
    end

    subgraph Extract
        B1[Parse PDF / DOCX / TXT]
        B2[Store text + metadata]
        B --> B1 --> B2
    end

    subgraph Summarize
        C1["Generate structured summary (skills, experience, projects)"]
        C2[OR create embeddings for vector DB]
        C --> C1
        C --> C2
    end

    subgraph Rank
        D1[Compare summary/embeddings with job requirements]
        D2[Compute score / rank]
        D3[Optional: LLM explains ranking]
        D --> D1 --> D2 --> D3
    end

    subgraph Store
        E1[DB table: screened_resumes]
        E2[Include summary, score, path, date]
        E --> E1 --> E2
    end

    subgraph Feedback
        F1[Track shortlisted / rejected]
        F2[Improve ranking or prompts]
        F --> F1 --> F2
    end
